statements.sql: select `types`.*, `services_types`.`service_id` as `pivot_service_id`, `services_types`.`type_id` as `pivot_type_id` from `types` inner join `services_types` on `types`.`id` = `services_types`.`type_id` where `services_types`.`service_id` in (6, 7, 10)

select `schedules`.*, `types`.`name` from `schedules` inner join `types` on `schedules`.`service_type_id` = `types`.`id` where `schedules`.`service_id` in (6, 7, 10) and date(`work_day`) >= '2021.03.19'
